       cryptographic functions.

       EEVVPP_SSeeaall... and EEVVPP_OOppeenn... provide public key encryption
       and decryption to implement digital "envelopes".

       The EEVVPP_SSiiggnn... and EEVVPP_VVeerriiffyy... functions implement
       digital signatures.

